Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
